Package: almanac
Title: Tools for Business Calendars
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Davis",
           family = "Vaughan",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "davis@rstudio.com")
Description: Provides tools for creating business calendars with 
    custom holidays. Calendars can then be used to shift dates or generate 
    sequences relative to that calendar.
